@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ojyphr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.99) - (v1 + 0.62 * tmp + 0.15)))
    v0 = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.84 - tmp + 0.01) / 0.90))
    v0 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.22 + tmp + 0.79)) / (wp.exp(v0 + 0.59) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.99)))
    tmp = 0.96
    tmp = 0.89
    tmp = wp.sin(v0)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.60)))
    tmp = 0.09
    data[tid] = v0
